field are excellent resources for internships and full time positions for current cadets Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Ethical   Legal How can you help  Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services  Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Ethical   Legal How can you help  Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Ethical   Legal How can you help  Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Academic Services   Support Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Career Services Home Cadets Cadets Employers Employers Alumni Alumni Faculty   Staff Ethical   Legal How can you help  Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Faculty   Staff Faculty   Staff Ethical   Legal How can you help  Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Ethical   Legal Ethical   Legal How can you help How can you help Recruiting Recruiting Alumni Career Vignettes Alumni Career Vignettes Family   Visitors Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Career Services Staff Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services Mrs Kaye Taylor            Contact Caree